=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201311/thumb_img/8_thumb_G_1384988790593.gif', 'images/201311/goods_img/8_G_1384988790722.jpg', 'images/201311/source_img/8_G_1384988790762.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '2', '1241425512', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1385075894', '9', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '', '0', '0', '', '', '0', '');
